# Atomic Arch AUR Supply-Chain Campaign - Snort 3 Rules
# Uncompiled: Snort 3 not available in this environment; structurally validated only.
# SID:2100201 - C2 callback (medium confidence: /api/agent is generic; C2 uses Tor onion service)
# SID:2100202 - Data exfil via temp.sh (medium confidence)
